data.description: A BOATER'S PARADISE- Fully Furnished! Discover this Impeccably Maintained Waterfront 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom CBS POOL Home, situated on a 1/2 acre in the Highly Desirable, North River Shores! This Home has it ALL! Offering your OWN Private Dock with Ocean Access- 16,000 lb Lift w/ Aluminum Bunks (Electric and Water at Dock), Impact Sliders- 2022, Metal Roof- 2016, S/S Appliances- 2018, New W/H- 2021, Updated Bathrooms, Vanities, Tile w/Glass Shower-2019, New 250 Gallon Propane Tank- 2020, New Paver Addition- 2021, Circular Driveway and so much more! This Magnificent Luxury Waterfront Home is a Lifestyle, step inside to an inviting open, very spacious Floor Plan and Living Area, with Coastal Decor and finishes, 4 Impact Sliders leading out to your outdoor Oasis, great for entertaining with Family and Friends, as you enjoy your morning coffee or afternoon cocktail. The Kitchen boasts 36-inch Wood Cabinets with Lighting, S/S Appliances, an Island, Wine Fridge, plenty of counterspace/storage and a Formal Dining Area. The Owners Suite is nestled in the back of the Home, opening up to your Pool/Patio area. Enjoy a short Boat ride to Waterfront Dining and come back Home to Breathtaking Sunsets by your Pool and Patio area, surrounded by Mature Palm Trees and Incredible Landscaping throughout the Property for added privacy, overlooking your huge Backyard to your Dock with Tiki Bar! North River Shores is conveniently located to Downtown Stuart with a private community Boat Ramp, Basketball Courts, & Playground. Just minutes from Local Beaches, Parks, Downtown Jensen/Stuart, endless shoppes/restaurants, A+ rated schools and much more! Paradise Awaits, don't miss your opportunity on this Waterfront Gem!
